@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_unxvww(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((0.86 / (v0 + 0.23 + v2 + 0.27)) - tmp)
    tmp = wp.cos(0.77)
    v2 = v1
    v0 = wp.abs((0.20 + (v0 + 0.35 - v0 + 0.19)))
    v1 = (tmp - tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
